{"tid":1623354,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[警世] 折衷方法 － (1) 全港水魔法/ (2) 暗地打狗/ (3) 腐敗高官 / (4) 用車","createTime":"2019-10-04T20:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:58:49.000Z","uid":71037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4eded47cd36192a2f3cc3899c61dc61041dc0cf0","tid":1623354,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:11:17.000Z","msg":"去到今時今日，有d 位真係好考驗大眾既智慧<br />\n我唔想帶錯風向做千古罪人，所以唔評論大肆裝修中資同藍屍店是否正確。<br />\n不過警告定大家唔好做犯法野呀！要做奉公守法好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我諗，可以全港用水魔法或者其他(例如傾倒英泥、廢料) 方法，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">唔一定下下爆玻璃又火魔法</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n(一) 水魔法<br />\n1. 同樣達到要中資同藍屍店<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">承受經濟損失</span></strong><br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">畫面較美觀</span></strong>，望落好過爆玻璃爆閘。<br />\n3. 南亞同其他用心不良者 (eg 強國大媽, 藍屍) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無得乘機偷野入示威者數</span></strong><br />\n4. 狗<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無得</span></strong>用搶劫合化法自己<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開槍殺人</span></strong><br />\n5. 無話一定用乾淨食水或淡水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加唔加料自行決定啦<br />\n6. 不怕影響國際輿論同觀感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31bfb39d65e295eaa761c8530bb4f4d6b4a48c3","tid":1623354,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:12:34.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"0cfeb74ab3e2ba2da685166b7a6381492db38d5f","tid":1623354,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:12:44.000Z","msg":"天佑香港"},{"pid":"77775e729856de21bd98f2d63c0fb0f9b88ad474","tid":1623354,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:13:02.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好做犯法野呀！要做奉公守法好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\